{"tid":2425539,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參觀駁二反送中運動展 高雄市長陳其邁雙手握拳撐香港","createTime":"2021-02-27T11:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-27T15:18:13.000Z","uid":337052,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"154004572e908f6dafe36d4b2099eeb29ce794cb","tid":2425539,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"x-large\">參觀駁二反送中運動展 陳其邁雙手握拳撐香港</span></strong><br />\n   <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/02/27/3451444_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F02%2F27%2F3451444_1_1.jpg&h=22f6ebfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳其邁在40公尺反送中布條前，雙手握拳比出加油手勢。（記者葛祐豪攝）<br />\n<br />\n2021/02/27 18:26<br />\n〔記者葛祐豪／高雄報導〕高雄市長陳其邁今天下午前往駁二參觀「若水，如火，有聲：一個關於行動的展覽」、「返校」等兩個展覽，他有感而發的說，<span class=\"red\">「若水，如火，有聲：一個關於行動的展覽」完整展出來自香港反送中運動現場的40公尺大型布條，分為「鏡頭的凝視」、「反抗的畫筆」、「我們皆在場」三個單元</span>，集結插畫、、攝影、雕塑、平面設計、獨立小誌等逾百件作品。陳其邁看得津津有味，並在反送中布條前，雙手握拳比出加油手勢。<br />\n<br />\n陳其邁在現場接受媒體聯訪時說，他剛剛先去看「返校」事件的展演，用電玩的安排，呈現過去的白色恐怖，台灣作為一個民主國家、對人權重視的國家，「返校」是過去式，是讓台灣人記住過去台灣在威權時期，對於人權、對於自由打壓的一個歷史錯誤，希望記取歷史的錯誤，深化台灣的民主。<br />\n<br />\n陳其邁表示<span class=\"red\">「若水」是在講香港，敘述香港人爭取自由民主的過程，從下而上，不屈不撓的抗爭，但也面臨包括中國國安法，及港府對香港人權自由的打壓。</span><br />\n<br />\n他強調：「這個是一個現在式」，從過去到現在，一方面讓台灣年輕人能知道，香港現在正發生什麼事情，就人權做為世界普世價值而言，<span class=\"red\">讓我們能夠珍惜現在的民主，因此特別來這裡，支持香港爭取自由民主。<br />\n</span><br />\n陳其邁透露，去年7月他在台北，跟主辦單位說是不是有一天來高雄，今天在高雄同樣把過去內容，利用駁二倉庫群展出，比台北做的更精緻、更有意義，展出的數量也比台北更多。<br />\n<br />\n陳其邁指出，<span class=\"red\">他覺得做為一個自由人、做為一個高雄人，可以來看看近水之隔的香港，正在發生那些事情，「讓我一起來支持香港的民主，一起來撐香港」。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3451444\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3451444&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm7c0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=52e1fa36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F3451444&h=10bea1e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/3451444</a>"},{"pid":"287e36a7472c2d74b245c994c7bf238df31843d8","tid":2425539,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:51:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/DGS0iGCxuh0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FDGS0iGCxuh0&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm7c0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=719d188b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/DGS0iGCxuh0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://pier2.org/exhibition/info/924/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpier2.org%2Fexhibition%2Finfo%2F924%2F&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm7c0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=4768da73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pier2.org/exhibition/info/924/</a>"},{"pid":"46336d3119895861a515a129d7a533b177001faf","tid":2425539,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:52:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.ncafroc.org.tw/files/event/20210113/3a610b85d17c4d53b2893f4d42f2e1fd/3a610b85d17c4d53b2893f4d42f2e1fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncafroc.org.tw%2Ffiles%2Fevent%2F20210113%2F3a610b85d17c4d53b2893f4d42f2e1fd%2F3a610b85d17c4d53b2893f4d42f2e1fd.jpg&h=8e731283&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ncafroc.org.tw/event_detail.html?id=297ef72276f145fb0176fb2ce7320021\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncafroc.org.tw%2Fevent_detail.html%3Fid%3D297ef72276f145fb0176fb2ce7320021&d=vb5EudyRk00tD8HubIiEm7c0zXsqQl3D3Nzt16t%2FTIU%3D&h=8c104845\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ncafroc.org.tw/event_detail.html?id=297ef72276f145fb0176fb2ce7320021</a>"},{"pid":"2fd7b909d13a31a65ca0e8931e19a768f802db3b","tid":2425539,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"最重要是台灣年輕人從現在的香港學到什麼，<br />\n<br />\n然後自己選擇未來是親共還是反共"},{"pid":"287a62ac699e75d92ca619b41e6b8a001008ad45","tid":2425539,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fd7b909d13a31a65ca0e8931e19a768f802db3b","tid":2425539,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"最重要是台灣年輕人從現在的香港學到什麼，<br />\n<br />\n然後自己選擇未來是親共還是反共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"說得好"},{"pid":"74ceca5f5d41efb599d4e5e28919c23c460ffc3c","tid":2425539,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ikh.tw/freshweekly/t_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ikh.tw%2Ffreshweekly%2Ft_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_.jpg&h=338ae9cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\">駁二特區「若水，如火，有聲：一個關於行動的展覽」呼應香港反送中</span></strong><br />\n 2021/02/03 高培德 1022<br />\n<br />\n高市駁二藝術特區攜手台灣新聞攝影協會、香港邊城青年合辦「若水，如火，有聲：一個關於行動的展覽」，即日起至3月14日在大勇區P3倉庫免費參觀，主題定為Be Water(若水)、Be Fire(如火)，呼應香港抗爭精神，規劃「反抗的畫筆」藝術創作、「鏡頭的凝視」新聞攝影、「我們皆在場」歷史對話等三大單元，匯集台港創作者大型布條、紀實照片及雕塑等超過100件作品，呈現抗爭事件、新聞攝影、藝術創作及出版紀錄，部分展品涉及國安法不克公開亮相，展示牆刻意留白凸顯，現場也首度揭密香港反送中長40公尺大型布條。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ikh.tw/freshweekly/t_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ikh.tw%2Ffreshweekly%2Ft_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_1.jpg&h=7631f68b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ikh.tw/freshweekly/t_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ikh.tw%2Ffreshweekly%2Ft_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_2.jpg&h=f8bef168&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港2019年3月發起反送中運動，6月爆發街頭抗爭事件，高市副市長史哲、文化局長王文翠等人2月3日觀展聽取策展人陳怡靜、莊坤儒導覽解說，史哲表示，港版國安法2020年6月過關，多數人權受到侵害，彰縣自由價值，展場留白部分強調人權可貴。<br />\n史哲在展區連儂牆寫下「自由無懼，人權無礙」，台灣先民開闢民主道路，高雄扮演民主進程重要角色，責無旁貸須持續聲援國際友人，創造美好社會傳承後代青年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ikh.tw/freshweekly/t_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ikh.tw%2Ffreshweekly%2Ft_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_3.jpg&h=3414f1f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ikh.tw/freshweekly/t_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ikh.tw%2Ffreshweekly%2Ft_freshweekly_p65g96yc99s7_4.jpg&h=3ed1f8ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n陳怡靜表示，藝術家用創作參與文化行動，試圖透過紀錄引導世界回顧抗爭中香港，莊坤儒也坦言台灣先民爭取新聞自由，無須擔心消逝不見，香港反送中事件衝突愈演愈烈，連媒體也遭受辣椒水無情攻擊。<br />\n配合展覽，同步規劃絹印工作坊、講座等系列活動，陳怡靜、莊坤儒2月6日下午3點現場導覽解說，相關展覽資訊可上官網查詢。圖與文／高培德"},{"pid":"a24e87524441498ba9f69a914b377d3624c228b8","tid":2425539,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:57:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1e1a0fb94e1cd730f0b8b62ff84322733ae4f9","tid":2425539,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2021/02/03/realtime/11475968.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;w=930&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2021%2F02%2F03%2Frealtime%2F11475968.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26w%3D930%26nt%3D1&h=ca4ce358&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1203c4e522c14b2f2cbe998dfc6022e1cac70e70","tid":2425539,"uid":221571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2fd7b909d13a31a65ca0e8931e19a768f802db3b","tid":2425539,"uid":70487,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:52:52.000Z","msg":"最重要是台灣年輕人從現在的香港學到什麼，<br />\n<br />\n然後自己選擇未來是親共還是反共"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-27T11:59:30.000Z","msg":"香港做哂示範俾全世界睇<br />\n然後佢地要點做都唔輪到我地控制<br />\n世界冇咁多個侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b943e5bbd52d18ab9676553e88239b69037dfb88","tid":2425539,"uid":51701,"like":0,"di